						 make changes to this lightbox outside of this div, those changes need to be made to every lightbox file within the
						 Molecules/10-lightbox folder. }}
						<p class="featured">Borrower repays the loan</p>
						<p>Lenders receive repayments over time, based on the given repayment schedule and the borrower’s
							ability to repay. The repayments go into the lenders’ Kiva accounts.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="dotted-line white"></div>
	<svg class="icon icon-repeat">
		<use xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" xlink:href="#icon-repeat"></use>
	</svg>
